A new video published by CNN appears to show Ukrainians destroying a weapon by the Russian military that rips the oxygen out of humans? lungs. Putin has been using thermobaric weapons to inflict massive casualties on the front lines. This weapon, banned by the Geneva Convention, can rip the oxygen out of people?s lungs when detonated. A Thermobaric weapon, also called an aerosol bomb, a vacuum bomb, or a fuel air explosive, is a type of explosive that uses oxygen from the surrounding air to generate a high-temperature explosion. The fuel?air explosive is one of the best-known types of thermobaric weapons  